---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Hero from '@/components/layout/Hero.astro';
import Callout from '@/components/content/Callout.astro';
import { GUIDE_PAGES } from '@/lib/constants';
---

<BaseLayout title="Decent Investing">
  <Hero />

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <h2 id="the-strategy" class="mb-4 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">
      The Strategy
    </h2>

    <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      Most people don't need a complicated financial plan. They need a clear sequence of simple
      steps — and the discipline to follow through.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      This guide covers the fundamentals that apply to the majority of people. If you have
      significant debt, complex tax situations, or unique circumstances, you should supplement this
      with professional advice from a
      <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fiduciary">fiduciary advisor</a>.
    </p>

    <ol class="mb-10 space-y-4">
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span
          class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sage-100 text-sm font-bold text-sage-700 dark:bg-sage-900/40 dark:text-sage-300"
          >0</span
        >
        <div>
          <a
            href="/guide/0-before-you-start"
            class="font-semibold text-sage-700 no-underline hover:underline dark:text-sage-400"
            >Figure out what matters to you</a
          >
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Start with purpose, not products.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span
          class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sage-100 text-sm font-bold text-sage-700 dark:bg-sage-900/40 dark:text-sage-300"
          >1</span
        >
        <div>
          <a
            href="/guide/1-cash-cushion"
            class="font-semibold text-sage-700 no-underline hover:underline dark:text-sage-400"
            >Build your cash cushion</a
          >
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            3 to 12 months of expenses, tiered for access and yield.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span
          class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sage-100 text-sm font-bold text-sage-700 dark:bg-sage-900/40 dark:text-sage-300"
          >2</span
        >
        <div>
          <a
            href="/guide/2-tackle-debt"
            class="font-semibold text-sage-700 no-underline hover:underline dark:text-sage-400"
            >Tackle high-interest debt</a
          >
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Pay off expensive debt before investing aggressively.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span
          class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sage-100 text-sm font-bold text-sage-700 dark:bg-sage-900/40 dark:text-sage-300"
          >3</span
        >
        <div>
          <a
            href="/guide/3-investment-accounts"
            class="font-semibold text-sage-700 no-underline hover:underline dark:text-sage-400"
            >Use the right accounts</a
          >
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Employer match &rarr; HSA &rarr; IRA &rarr; 401k &rarr; taxable.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span
          class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sage-100 text-sm font-bold text-sage-700 dark:bg-sage-900/40 dark:text-sage-300"
          >4</span
        >
        <div>
          <a
            href="/guide/4-investment-choices"
            class="font-semibold text-sage-700 no-underline hover:underline dark:text-sage-400"
            >Pick simple investments</a
          >
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Low-cost index funds. Understand fees. Add bonds.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span
          class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sage-100 text-sm font-bold text-sage-700 dark:bg-sage-900/40 dark:text-sage-300"
          >5</span
        >
        <div>
          <a
            href="/guide/5-staying-the-course"
            class="font-semibold text-sage-700 no-underline hover:underline dark:text-sage-400"
            >Stay the course</a
          >
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Markets drop. That's normal. Don't panic.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li class="flex gap-3">
        <span
          class="flex h-8 w-8 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-sage-100 text-sm font-bold text-sage-700 dark:bg-sage-900/40 dark:text-sage-300"
          >6</span
        >
        <div>
          <a
            href="/guide/6-next-steps"
            class="font-semibold text-sage-700 no-underline hover:underline dark:text-sage-400"
            >Take your next steps</a
          >
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
            Automate, name beneficiaries, review annually.
          </p>
        </div>
      </li>
    </ol>

    <Callout type="tip" title="The 85% Solution">
      <p>
        Getting started at 85% right is vastly better than waiting to be 100% optimized. Open an
        account this week. Set up an automatic transfer. You can fine-tune later — the important
        thing is to start.
      </p>
    </Callout>

    <div class="mt-10 text-center">
      <a
        href="/guide/0-before-you-start"
        class="inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-sage-600 px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white no-underline transition-colors hover:bg-sage-700 dark:bg-sage-700 dark:text-white dark:hover:bg-sage-600"
      >
        Start the Guide &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
